    dc:description "Figures 84 - 91. Amauromyza flavifrons (Meigen), head 84 anterior 85 lateral 86, 87 Amauromyza karli (Hendel), head 86 dorsal 87 lateral 88 Aulagromyza nitida (Malloch), male, lateral 89 Aulagromyza tridentata (Loew), male, lateral 90, 91 Calycomyza enceliae Spencer, male, on bush sunflower (R. Hemberger - California, Irvine)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/572110" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1051.64603.figures418-424>
    dc:description "Figures 418 - 424. Amauromyza flavifrons (Meigen), male genitalia 418 ejaculatory apodeme 419 external genitalia, anterior (subepandrial sclerite shaded) 420 external genitalia, ventral 421 hypandrium and postgonite, ventral 422 postgonite, lateral 423 phallus, ventral 424 phallus, left lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/572173" ;
